<%= provide(:body_id, 'param-setting') %>
<%= provide(:result, '系统说明') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>查看关联信息</h1>

        <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
          <div class="span12">
            <p>
              可以查看所以已关联的出口的用户信息，也可以进行删除等操作。<br/>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p></p>


        <p class="hidden-phone">
          <a class="btn btn-info btn-large pull-right">详细指南请猛击此处 &raquo;</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
     <div class="span12">
       <ul class="breadcrumb">
         <li>
           <a href="/">
             <i class="radmin-icon radmin-home"></i>
             首页
           </a>
           <span class="divider">/</span>
         </li>
         <li>
           <a href="mng_user">
             <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
             管理系统用户
           </a>
           <span class="divider">/</span>
         </li>
         <li class="active">
           <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
           查看关联信息
         </li>
       </ul>
     </div>
   </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
        <div class="span12">
          <h4 class="title">关联信息</h4>

          <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
          <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-radmin">
            <thead>
            <tr style="text-align:center;">
              <th style="text-align:center;">出口编号</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">出口名称</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">用户名称</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">Email</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">联系电话</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">操作选项</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <% @en.each do |x| %>
              <tr>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= x.alias %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= x.name %></td>
                <% if x.user.blank? %>
                  <td style="text-align:center;"></td>
                  <td style="text-align:center;"></td>
                  <td style="text-align:center;"></td>
                  <td style="text-align:center;"></td>

                <% else %>
                  <td style="text-align:center;"><%= x.user.alias %></td>
                  <td style="text-align:center;"><%= x.user.email %></td>
                  <td style="text-align:center;"><%= x.user.contact %></td>
                  <td style="text-align:center;">
                    <a class="btn btn-small btn-danger" href="del_interaction?id=<%= x.id %>">
                      <i class="icon-trash icon-white"></i>
                      删除
                    </a>
                <% end %>

                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>


            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          当一切似乎毫无希望时，我看着切石工人在他的石头上，敲击了上百次，而不见任何裂痕出现。
          但在第一百零一次时，石头被劈成两半。我体会到，并非那一击，而是前面的敲打使它裂开。
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">贾柯·瑞斯</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>